s anticipated or when combined with other agents that can cause hypomagnesemia such as diuretics, aminoglycosides, cation exchange resins, amphotericin B, cetuximab, cisplatin, cyclosporine, foscarnet, panitumumab, pentamidine, and tacrolimus.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/105605/', '', 'Tinidazole, Levofloxacin, Tetracycline, Sucralfate, Misoprostol, Bismuth subcitrate potassium, Metronidazole, Famotidine, Rifabutin, Cimetidine, Nizatidine, More', '', 1767369485);
